context_38015=This monk was one of the attackers. You pressed him further about the antidote, and the monk said there was none. However, you found a letter from the monk, where he said that he resented Shaolin since he has been defeated by Shaolin disciples so many times. He then decided to steal a script from Shaolin. It also mentioned the Dharmapala Ni Ma's meeting place in a riddle.
context_38019=<s>Is this riddle "Random light spot, only one star" the place where to exchange Scripts? Can Elder Brother and Martial Uncle guess it? I should ask more people about it.
