accept_38056_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Yong Yi used to be Mount Song Sword Sect's disciple. We should inform the Headmaster of Mount Song Sword Sect. I heard the new headmaster Zuo Yuelin has great ambitions. He aims to rebuild Mount Song Sword Sect's reputation. But his behavior is not righteous.</font>
accept_38061_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Now I don't worry. Previously I sent Qingyuan to Mount Song Sword Sect regarding Yong Yi's case. Then a Mount Song disciple sent a letter, saying that Shaolin plans to take Yong Yi into the temple by force, so Mount Song puts Qingyuan into prison. They will release Qingyuan in exchange for Yong Yi.</font>
accept_38065_1=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Mount Song Sword Sect must have more patrolling disciples now. Just now I sent Qingkong to investigate the surrounding area of Mount Song Sword Sect. Now he should be waiting for you at the foot of mountain. Go and inform the Welcoming Monk first, and go to Qingkong to hear the details. Then head to Mount Song Sword Sect and rescue Qingyuan as soon as possible.</font>
complete_38056=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Mount Song Sword Sect and Shaolin never get along. Hopefully Qingyuan will not cause extra conflicts on this trip. Right now Yong Yi is badly injured. He is resting in the Herbal Store.</font>
complete_38065=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >You are finally here! Evil Mount Song Sword Sect! They've put me into prison without reasons. They even sent </font> <font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >people</font>  <font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >to guard here</font>.
complete_38066=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Where did you come from? Did you come from Shaolin? How dare you come to Mount Song Sword Sect alone? You think there is no one in Mount Song Sword Sect?</font>
complete_38095=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >The one behind ruining Shaolin's reputation this time is Mount Song Sword Sect. It seems their Headmaster Zuo is very manipulative. To prevent Wulin getting affected, I think we should put this case aside for now. I will send a letter to Mount Song Sword Sect. If they execute such an evil manipulation again to harm Shaolin, we will not let it slide. Hopefully Headmaster Zuo will stop. If they stop the evil deeds, we will not cause trouble and we shall be friendly.</font>
complete_38423=<s>Spare my life please! I'll confess! The Wanderers Valley people who were killed in Shaolin were actually poisoned to death by the Royal Guard. <BR><s>I just heard that the Royal Guard General, who is responsible for contacting spies in many schools, is in Yanjing Ancient Tomb Sect to meet a Beggar's Sect Spy. If you want more details, go find him. I am only a minion.
context_38056=<s>Yong Yi used to be Mount Song Sword Sect's disciple. We should go inform the Headmaster of Mount Song Sword Sect. I heard the new headmaster Zuo Yuelin has great ambitions. He aims to rebuild Mount Song Sword Sect's reputation. But his behavior is not righteous. Ask Qingyuan to head down the mountain. Ask him to tell Headmaster Zuo that Yong Yi joined Shaolin. Ask him to come back quickly and be careful. Here is the Red Blood Circulation Invigorating Pill. Let Yong Yi take it first. It can help to stop the pain.
context_38061=Now I don't worry. Previously I sent Qingyuan to Mount Song Sword Sect for Yong Yi's case. Then a Mount Song disciple sent a letter, saying that Shaolin plans to take Yong Yi into the temple by force, so Mount Song put Qingyuan into prison. They will release Qingyuan in exchange for Yong Yi. Yong Yi is badly injured and I promised him the entry to Shaolin. How can I change my promise? The righteous is in everyone's heart. Deal with affairs appropriately. Please head down the mountain and rescue Qingyuan.
context_38065=<s>Mount Song Sword Sect must have more patrolling disciples now. Just now I sent Qingkong to investigate the surrounding area of Mount Song Sword Sect. Now he should be waiting for you at the foot of mountain. Go and inform the Welcoming Monk first, and go to Qingkong to hear the details. Then head to Mount Song Sword Sect and rescue Qingyuan as soon as possible.
context_38066=<s>The Mount Song Sword Sect Disciples nearby always say bad things about us Shaolin. Their guard is always up. My leg is injured. Only if you defeat them, then we can safely leave.
context_38255=<s>Even though Qing se hides in the Back Mountain, I don't think Xingxiu Sect people will stop. Quickly find Elder Kong.
context_38258=<s>We the Xingxiu Sect have always been known as an evil school in Jianghu. Over the past few days since I came here, I found many people wanted to kill me. If you don't want me to trouble the villagers, help me kill those Jianghu wanderers first. They are not good people. You should not feel troubled.
context_38264=<s>Shaolin is in such a disaster. I think Bai Zhenzhen will come back again after sobering up. The only way out is that you go to Xingxiu Sect in Evil Men's Valley. Hopefully their leader Su Bailing can solve this issue.
context_38266=<s>It's not hard for us to help Shaolin. We don't really care to get involved with Shaolin. But as you know, we Xingxiu Sect do things at a cost. How about this? Pass my message to the Immortal. Let him decide.
context_38267=<s>Recently, Suyun Palace and I are discussing the issue about land division. A moment ago a disciple said they found some Suyun Palace disciples near Xingxiu Sect. Go defeat them for me.
context_38400=<s>Go to Yanjing Ancient Tomb Sect. Investigate whether there are still people who use this poison.
context_38402=<s>Okay. We the Ancient Tomb Sect always keep our promises. Go ahead and you will find my Elder Sister Lu.
context_38403=<s>You came from Shaolin, right? I heard all the martial arts in the world come from Shaolin. But I don't believe our martial arts in Ancient Tomb Sect are inferior to Shaolin. If you want to meet my master, defeat me first.
submit_38066=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >Calm down. You must be Mount Song Sword Sect's swordsman Mr. Zuo. Glad to meet you.</font>
