complete_38379=<s>In fact, this is a Seven Colors Hell conspiracy. I was in their grip and they wanted me to help them blend into the royal residence to assault the emperor because I originally got word that the emperor would be returning to Lord Yan's Residence that night. <BR><s>Those Scholars are the ones I deliberately captured to deceive the residence manager.
complete_38414=<s>Recently, in Jianghu, Wanderer's Valley and Royal Guards often fight with each other, sending people to assault each other's disciples. In fact, they are no good people, let them kill each other. I'm just watching the show. Anyway, our Beggar's Sect will always be the best faction in the world. Haha...
complete_38437=<s>Why are there killers all of a sudden? Are they sent by Jiang Tianao?
context_38180=<s>You go back and tell that old jerk that I will never forgive him in my life. His head will roll. I will definitely get my revenge! Get out of my way too!
context_38305=<s>This poisonous creature is an ancient poisonous beast. It is not to be underestimated. Collect some withered branches. We will use smoke to draw it out of the cave. The attack is bound to be half the effort.
context_38331=<s>The time is ripe for us to prepare to draw out that poisonous creature and attack it again.
context_38442=<s>Jiang Tianao, that Jianghu degenerate, has wounded my wife. We cannot exist together! I must take his head to avenge my wife!
context_38479=<s>You caught me. Remember, I will never be a man unless I take revenge. Ten years later when I am strong again, I will get my revenge to you! You broke my passion! Die, bald ass! Poo-poo!
